embeddings.name: End-to-End Test for Findigs Rental Application

steps.name: user enters valid firstname, lastname, email, phone
user clicks on Create an Account button
user is redirected to phone verification page
user is successfully navigated to Property Search page and is able to see welcoming message
user selects Auto City to filter search results
user selects first apartment in the list
user clicks on Ready to Apply button
user is able to click on Change Property option
user selects Auto City to filter search results
user selects second apartment in the list
user selects move-in date the first date of the next month
user is able to click on Start Application button and verify this button is enabled
